Introduction

Lee Ye Dam is a South Korean Singer under ARMADA Ent. He is the Maknae of the boy group ONE PACT.

Prior to this, he shot to fame after participating in the survival shows "Loud" in 2021, "Boys Planet" in 2022, and in the show "Show King Night" in 2023.

On October 5, 2023, Armada Entertainment revealed Yedam as the Fourth Member of their upcoming boy group ONE PACT.
